name: OutdoorActivityPicker
0:
”Alexa, open outdoor activity picker”
”Alexa, start outdoor activity picker”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: outdoor activity picker
des:
Next time you want to go do something outdoors, but can't or simply don't want to make a decision on what to do, just make Alexa choose for you! 

At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
